{"tid":602195,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【台媒訪問】李嘉誠：港府公屋做不好　打不開社會死結","createTime":"2018-03-23T00:15:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T02:38:36.000Z","uid":48083,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0436a4c2c844fa05af74e67aae2bd30fa4735e7d","tid":602195,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T00:15:50.000Z","msg":"長和（001）主席李嘉誠接受台灣《商業週刊》書面訪問時，再提及本港樓市問題。他指出香港樓價在過去兩年大升了一倍，現在樓價已與普羅市民的收入出現脫節，因此香港樓市需要多建公屋，讓市民大眾不會因為住屋問題而令生活出現困難。<br />\n<br />\n李嘉誠說：「今時今日，做官不容易，做老百姓也不容易，房屋是衣食住行的基本需要之一，而很多政府，就如香港政府一樣，需要靠房產業增加收入，房價便難以達到一個人人也能承擔的水平；位置較理想的地段，供不應求價更高。因此，政府要做的，就是要滿足公共房屋的需要，這方面政府做不好，打不開死結。」<br />\n<br />\n蘋果財經，關心你飯碗<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/appledailyatm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fappledailyatm&d=tbxbV0lixDOzE9Xmr3OJm75jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=a0131e2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/appledailyatm</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180322/57981926\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180322%2F57981926&d=tbxbV0lixDOzE9Xmr3OJm75jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=2a183b5c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180322%2F57981926&h=d8690bb4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180322/57981926</a>"},{"pid":"4b712eb5ff06befbfa6373a8f981b4aad8203aef","tid":602195,"uid":97551,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T01:28:41.000Z","msg":"多建公屋比真香港人住<br />\n<br />\n剩係起公屋，但比新移民住都係無撚用"},{"pid":"9e946502a86f5f505b4ecc47eba0bf2853afe867","tid":602195,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":32,"score":-32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T01:29:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6026d4746ea8755b1de23af8b15ad51c3ede206a","tid":602195,"uid":29270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T01